ELINSKY, Respondent, v. STUYVESANT INS. CO., Appellant. (City Court of New York,

General Term.

January, 1902.) Action by Meyer Elinsky against the Stuyvesant Insurance Company of the city of New York. Maxwell Hall Elliott, for appellant. Alexander Rosenthal, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
